node.title: Police locate Auckland man missing since Monday
node.description: Police say Auckland man Nicholas Nadin, who was reported missing on Monday, has been located safe and well today.
node.content:
["Police say Auckland man Nicholas Nadin, who was reported missing on Monday, has been located safe and well today.", "", "
Aucklander Nicholas Nadin had been missing since 17 January. Photo: Supplied / NZ Police
", "The 52-year-old Bucklands Beach man had been missing since 17 January.", "Police thanked the public for their assistance in locating Nadin."]
